      <bioghist id="aspace_c064f8bfb3c39d57778823844d4e584f">
         <head>Katherine Heinemann</head>
         <p>Katherine Heinemann, American poet. Heinemann was born in St. Louis and attended Washington University.</p>  
      </bioghist>
